title: Mistral AI surfs vibe-coding tailwinds with new coding models
description: French AI startup Mistral today launched Devstral 2, a new generation of its AI model designed for coding, as the company seeks to catch up to bigger AI labs like Anthropic and other coding-focused LLMs.
